s of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/110463/', '', 'Risperidone', 'Methotrimeprazine, Triflupromazine, Promazine', 1767369485);
