cts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/110495/', '', 'Amisulpride, Pimavanserin', 'Thiopental, Ethchlorvynol, Dichloralphenazone, Ephedrine, Tropicamide, Phenylephrine, Aprepitant', 1767369485);
